    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exceptional caliber, maintained in impeccable showroom condition. This specimen exhibits no discernible wear, reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship and uncompromising care. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, adheres to the highest standards of automotive excellence. Mechanically, the vehicle performs with the precision and reliability one expects from a premier acquisition. We invite the most discerning collectors and enthusiasts to experience this peerless example of engineering and design.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
