      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. It has been pampered since day one and is in truly flawless shape\u2014it honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and kept in pristine condition, this is definitely the one for you. It's a total dream to drive, and I'd love for it to go to a great new home. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
