      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This investment-grade E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. The S54 3.2L straight-six remains in peak mechanical health, featuring a fully documented VANOS overhaul and shim-adjusted valve clearances. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed longitudinal gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis has been meticulously preserved, including proactive subframe reinforcement and a full suspension refresh with OEM components to maintain original dampening characteristics. The exterior retains its factory luster with zero signs of oxidation, while the interior features immaculate Nappa leather and functional bolsters. This is a turn-key example for a collector who demands mechanical perfection and structural integrity.",
